Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…做出了错误的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…想要去相信伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家全都被我害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我从一开始就相信自己并去战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是从一开始就把这家伙宰了的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那时  我变身为巨人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在更早的时间点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那时候就去战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能得到利威尔兵长的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还能抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做就做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我…我的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的选择  大家都丧命了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我  大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…果然…都是你的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我这双手恢复之后！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把你大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后细细地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕成一小块一小块
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一口一口地吃掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把艾伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把艾伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么刀刃砍不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对…还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦绝对还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要杀了这个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她全身上下都切开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把艾伦从那肮脏的地方救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你再稍微…等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且退下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持这个距离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度看上去并没有那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像连同整个后脖颈一起咬走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦死了吗
